  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate Long-term Outcomes following treatment with
      ABT-450/r/ABT-267, ABT-333 with or without RBV in Adults With Genotype 1 Chronic Hepatitis C
      Virus (HCV) Infection
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
